avorite melle or Ive been told, but can wizards tear some stuff up or what? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usarisparkles.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sari Sparkles</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/30/02 3:09:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=639.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PvP as a wizard</span><hr size=1> Might wanna ask on a wizard board ;p<br>
<br>
But wizards are great gankers, prolly the best. They are not duelers however. There's alot of little tricks to surviving as a wiz, that's why you should ask wizards, not rogues. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upiekrust.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PiekRust</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/30/02 3:57:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=639.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PvP as a wizard</span><hr size=1> lemme tell ya something:<br>
<br>
Wizards are very effective pkers in a few situations.<br>
<br>
1) They are the Attackie:  This means that the other person we'll just call PK01 isn't the one who initiates fight.  This gives the wizard the ability to have max casting range and posibly get off 2 nukes before the person realizes they are under seige. Sometimes they may attempt to stick a root (would be smart if the person isn't pking but in full exp gear and less MR) than nuke.  <br>
<br>
But if PK01 initiates fight caster/melee they have upperhand, a. Melees are up where they need to be to do damage, (sitting casters are a rogues dream when it comes to pk! Trust me, you do major major damage majorly fast and surpise people to the point where they have no idea what is going on.  If your a lighty rogue, use DE illusion in OT, apply a poison, walk up behind an exp group, stand still, backstab caster, hit em with poison, i use snaring poisons, and they ain't gonna get away!), or b. Casters like chanters can tash and mez you before you can cast your nuke, then they'll just nuke/mez/mana tap you so you can't do crap.  Necros will fully dot you and than get outta your casting range.<br>
<br>
2) Group PK<br>
<br>
Wizards are very effective in group pk and let me tell you why:<br>
<br>
Lets say your pking with an SK since you say its favorable class.  The SK initiates fight with another melee and the melee chases them to continue fight.  Then the unsuspecting melee runs straight into an ambush with a wizard floating up on a wall (wall bug helps here to lol), and gets nuked to high hell.  Ive done this with a wizard friend, they get ks but its so much fun to see these peoples reactions.  You get the cussers, the pleaders, and the laughers, THe laughers are always the best due to they can actually get a crack outta what just happened, those are the fun kills.<br>
<br>
Situations Wizards aren't good PKers:<br>
<br>
* When you get jumped my melees and your gate is interuppted.<br>
<br>
* When your in a indoor situation (ie deep in LGUK) and your not AA point sufficient for run speed.  Melees will tear you apart in confined indoor zones.<br>
<br>
* W/out epic it can be hard to get an edge in pk.  The Damage Absorb can sometimes save your life.<br>
<br>
Hope that helps ya out.<br>
<br>
As for not being able to duel....<br>
<br>
If your not in an arena and on a hilly area, they can kick your ass in a duel, but this isn't a dueling server we are talking about, this is a Zek. <p><font size=2><font color="yellow"><font face="arial narrow">Piek Rust
