<b> Lagrima Reveals the Truth!</b>: <img src="http://piecrust.50megs.com/lagrima1.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usarisparkles.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sari Sparkles</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/30/02 4:14:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=639.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PvP as a wizard</span><hr size=1> By gankers and not duelers I meant that wizards rely on the element of surpise, catching their opponent unprepared.<br>
